{"tid":910671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因航變廉價on99 預先揀位變要收費","createTime":"2018-11-21T10:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T15:29:48.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e236744787364a8cd7ea9a3efc84eb07219dd00d","tid":910671,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"「預選座位」將為您帶來不一樣的飛行體驗。即使選乘我們*的經濟客艙，您亦可以確保能夠與朋友或家人同坐，或預留您的首選座位，而無需等待至辦理登機手續時才選擇座位。<br />\n<br />\n選乘較高票價經濟客艙的乘客，馬可孛羅會銀卡及以上之會員或「寰宇一家」紅寶石及以上之會員可免費提前預選一般座位。<br />\n<br />\n我們現將「預選座位」服務函蓋至Economy Super Saver、Economy Save及fanfares機票，並將成為收費服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee284585bc522116a1fb263bb0115e291c62d5c","tid":910671,"uid":172379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e20d934c1d556ab486ab33b13d2daa681e2e4008","tid":910671,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"買貴飛咪有得免費㨂位<br />\n即係要你俾多D錢 唔係點填期油筆數<br />\n<br />\n無錢就唔好搭因航<br />\n<br />\n利申：窮鬼 好耐無搭過因航"},{"pid":"71bcd42579c2438c713b0e2e651a8a8d6abdb57a","tid":910671,"uid":85591,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:04.000Z","msg":"本身已經貴過人一大截，而家仲要巧立名目咁收費，遲早聽執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734ef850d2d3db8e7eb5a84cb638785c3fdcbef0","tid":910671,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"咁同廉航加飛機餐加飲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 機上娛我有ipad mbp switch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本唔撚需要佢"},{"pid":"5347f6d21e7854c41950abc2a9425125726a9211","tid":910671,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:54:27.000